@Steve L

Right? I went across first, entered ABYSS and then went on to complete the puzzle. I know nothing about calculus, neither in Polish nor in English, so when I got MAXIMUS from the crosses I just accepted it. I needed autocheck to sort out the mess that resulted.

I like your suggestion of adding "poetically" to the clue for ABYSM. I mean, it would not have helped me, as I just did not know the word, but surely some people would have been alerted to the fact that ABYSs was wrong.

@Mike 

